sets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e81fe1d3f9fd2a26736963a3b56572dd2ed34606","tid":172291,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T23:20:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n職業無分貴賤"},{"pid":"d28027d2e80b301ce2009104a6163d48dee2a440","tid":172291,"uid":72761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T23:21:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>多唔多人買套 有冇見過靚女自己買套</blockquote><br />\n未見過靚女買 不過見過一次有女嚟買 多數都係啲仔嚟買 條女就係岀面等 不過通常嚟買套嘅都係啲死廢老</blockquote><br />\n 見到人地買套個陣你諗緊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無咩特別野諗 不過會專登收錢收慢啲 等其他人見到個客買套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"483a28a40a9989d06e6e896adba05f786036c314","tid":172291,"uid":84426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T10:57:27.000Z","msg":"返七仔溝唔溝到女？係客定同事？"},{"pid":"e258d19c808a952d45a0da744d3bf2344cb3a26a","tid":172291,"uid":72761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:50:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>返七仔溝唔溝到女？係客定同事？</blockquote><br />\n未見過成功溝到女嘅例子 因為我間鋪比較少女仔翻 客嘅話 通常都會做到朋友 不過唔會太熟 都係見到就傾一兩句"}]}